---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="My Journey - Why I Started Creating This Website"
  description="A personal reflection on the journey of creating this website - from the initial spark of an idea to embracing uncertainty and growth. Join me as I explore the intersection of technology learning and personal expression."
>
  <!-- Structured Data for Journey Page -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    "name": "My Journey - Why I Started Creating This Website",
    "description": "A personal reflection on the journey of creating this website - from the initial spark of an idea to embracing uncertainty and growth.",
    "url": "https://palchat.org/journey",
    "mainEntity": {
      "@type": "Article",
      "name": "Why I Started Creating This Website",
      "author": {
        "@type": "Person",
        "name": "HumaneStack"
      },
      "datePublished": "2024-01-15",
      "dateModified": "2024-01-15",
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "HumaneStack"
      }
    },
    "inLanguage": "en-US"
  })}>
  </script>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background with animated elements -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 via-white to-purple-50 dark:from-gray-900 dark:via-gray-800 dark:to-gray-900"></div>
    
    <!-- Floating geometric shapes -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-20 h-20 bg-blue-200/30 dark:bg-blue-800/20 rounded-full animate-pulse-slow"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-40 right-20 w-16 h-16 bg-purple-200/30 dark:bg-purple-800/20 rounded-full animate-pulse-slow" style="animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-1/4 w-12 h-12 bg-green-200/30 dark:bg-green-800/20 rounded-full animate-pulse-slow" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-40 right-1/3 w-24 h-24 bg-yellow-200/30 dark:bg-yellow-800/20 rounded-full animate-pulse-slow" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Journey path illustration -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
      <svg class="w-full h-full max-w-4xl opacity-10" viewBox="0 0 800 400" fill="none">
        <path d="M50 200 Q200 100 350 200 T650 200" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-dasharray="10,5" class="text-blue-500"/>
        <circle cx="50" cy="200" r="8" fill="currentColor" class="text-blue-600"/>
        <circle cx="350" cy="200" r="8" fill="currentColor" class="text-purple-600"/>
        <circle cx="650" cy="200" r="8" fill="currentColor" class="text-green-600"/>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="animate-fade-in-up">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          My Journey
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Why I Started Creating This Website
        </p>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-500 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      
      <!-- Introduction -->
      <div class="mb-16 animate-fade-in-up">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">The Beginning</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            This is a story about learning, growth, and embracing uncertainty. It's about how a simple desire to understand technology led to something much more meaningful.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Journey Steps -->
      <div class="space-y-12">
        
        <!-- Step 1: The Spark -->
        <div class="animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-purple-50 dark:from-blue-900/20 dark:to-purple-900/20 rounded-2xl p-8 h-full">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm">1</div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">The Spark of an Idea</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                  The basic thought was simple: I wanted to learn technology. But I wasn't sure how to go about it. I had no clear goal or vision for how to apply what I was learning. That's when it struck me—why not create something I could play with? And so, this website was born. That's where the journey started. The rest is a story only time can tell.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
              <div class="relative">
                <div class="w-full h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-purple-100 dark:from-blue-800/30 dark:to-purple-800/30 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-32 h-32 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-8 h-8 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2: What This Website Is About -->
        <div class="animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-blue-50 dark:from-green-900/20 dark:to-blue-900/20 rounded-2xl p-8 h-full">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm">2</div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">What Is This Website About?</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                  At this starting point, the website is simply a reflection of my inner self—a personal blog, a digital mirror of my thoughts and evolution.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
              <div class="relative">
                <div class="w-full h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-100 to-blue-100 dark:from-green-800/30 dark:to-blue-800/30 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-32 h-32 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 w-6 h-6 bg-blue-400 rounded-full animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3: Why Not Just Write a Book -->
        <div class="animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 dark:from-purple-900/20 dark:to-pink-900/20 rounded-2xl p-8 h-full">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm">3</div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Why Not Just Write a Book or Blog Elsewhere?</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                  Because I also want to learn and play with technology. Creating this website allows me to both express myself and explore the world of web development at the same time. It's a form of creative freedom merged with technical growth.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
              <div class="relative">
                <div class="w-full h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-100 to-pink-100 dark:from-purple-800/30 dark:to-pink-800/30 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-32 h-32 text-purple-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute -top-2 -left-2 w-4 h-4 bg-pink-400 rounded-full animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4: Embracing Uncertainty -->
        <div class="animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-50 to-orange-50 dark:from-yellow-900/20 dark:to-orange-900/20 rounded-2xl p-8 h-full">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm">4</div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">What If I Don't Know Where This Will Go?</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                  That's perfectly fine. I don't know what the future of this website is. I've deliberately left it open, allowing time and experience to shape its direction. I'm here to ride the waves and enjoy the process.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
              <div class="relative">
                <div class="w-full h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-100 to-orange-100 dark:from-yellow-800/30 dark:to-orange-800/30 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-32 h-32 text-yellow-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 w-5 h-5 bg-orange-400 rounded-full animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 1.5s;"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 5: What If I Lose Interest -->
        <div class="animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-pink-50 dark:from-red-900/20 dark:to-pink-900/20 rounded-2xl p-8 h-full">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm">5</div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">What If I Lose Interest One Day?</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                  Honestly, I don't think I'll feel sad or regretful. Right now, it's just a journey I'm starting—a journey I want to experience, not analyze for profits, likes, or recognition. If it ends, it ends. And that's okay.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
              <div class="relative">
                <div class="w-full h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-100 to-pink-100 dark:from-red-800/30 dark:to-pink-800/30 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-32 h-32 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 w-6 h-6 bg-pink-400 rounded-full animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 0.8s;"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 6: Growth and Change -->
        <div class="animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.6s;">
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-blue-50 dark:from-indigo-900/20 dark:to-blue-900/20 rounded-2xl p-8 h-full">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm">6</div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">What If My Thinking Changes Over Time?</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                  That would be wonderful—because that is growth. When experiences shift your mindset, that's when true transformation happens.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
              <div class="relative">
                <div class="w-full h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-100 to-blue-100 dark:from-indigo-800/30 dark:to-blue-800/30 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-32 h-32 text-indigo-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -left-3 w-7 h-7 bg-blue-400 rounded-full animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 1.2s;"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 7: The Philosophy -->
        <div class="animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.7s;">
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50 to-green-50 dark:from-teal-900/20 dark:to-green-900/20 rounded-2xl p-8 h-full">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm">7</div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Why Do Experiences Change the Way We Think?</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                  Maybe that's what life is all about. We often assume the ending before the journey even begins. If things go as expected, the path feels smooth and pleasant. But when they don't, the journey can feel like a burden.
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
                  Instead, I try to begin with a blank page—letting time fill it with stories, emotions, learnings, and surprises. Whether the path is smooth or rough, it changes me. And that, I believe, is always beautiful.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
              <div class="relative">
                <div class="w-full h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-100 to-green-100 dark:from-teal-800/30 dark:to-green-800/30 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-32 h-32 text-teal-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-8 h-8 bg-green-400 rounded-full animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Conclusion -->
      <div class="mt-16 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.8s;">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white text-center">
          <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Journey Continues</h3>
            <p class="text-lg opacity-90 leading-relaxed">
              This website is more than just a project—it's a living document of growth, learning, and the beautiful uncertainty of life. Every line of code, every word written, is a step forward in this journey of discovery.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-6">
              <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-white text-blue-600 font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all duration-300">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path>
                </svg>
                Join the Conversation
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Journey Timeline Visualization -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-fade-in-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">The Journey So Far</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">A visual representation of the growth and evolution</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Timeline line -->
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-1 h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-500 via-purple-500 to-green-500"></div>
        
        <!-- Timeline items -->
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-1/2 pr-8 text-right">
              <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">The Spark</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Initial desire to learn technology</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-blue-500 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-gray-900 shadow-lg"></div>
            <div class="w-1/2 pl-8"></div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-1/2 pr-8"></div>
            <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-purple-500 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-gray-900 shadow-lg"></div>
            <div class="w-1/2 pl-8">
              <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">The Creation</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Building this website as a learning platform</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-1/2 pr-8 text-right">
              <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">The Growth</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Embracing uncertainty and change</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-green-500 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-gray-900 shadow-lg"></div>
            <div class="w-1/2 pl-8"></div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-1/2 pr-8"></div>
            <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-gray-900 shadow-lg animate-pulse"></div>
            <div class="w-1/2 pl-8">
              <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">The Future</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Continuing the journey with an open mind</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout> 